text: Pedro Sánchez (born 22 February 1966) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Murcia
